{
  "texts": [
    "Combining the 1,140 bot accounts with the 1,140 human ones results in our benchmark dataset: the fox8-23 dataset, which is publicly available at github.com/osome-iu/AIBot_fox8.",
    "In this section, we characterize the fox8 bots to reveal their behavioral patterns.",
    "Let us start with fox8 profiles and show the distributions of their follower/following count, tweet count, and creation year in Figure 1.",
    "These bots have 74.0 (SD=36.7) followers, 140.4 (SD=236.6) friends, and 149.6 (SD 178.8) tweets on average.",
    "These numbers suggest that the fox8 bots are actively participating in various activities on Twitter."
  ]
}